<!-- ║  TAB 3: TRANSFER IN PLAN ALGORITHM                              ║ -->
<!-- ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝ -->
<div class="tab-pane fade" id="tabTrfAlgo">

    <!-- Algorithm Overview -->
    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-3">
        <div class="card-header bg-success bg-opacity-10"><h5 class="card-title mb-0 text-success"><i class="bi bi-arrow-left-right me-2"></i>Transfer In Plan — Complete Algorithm</h5></div>
        <div class="card-body small">
            <p><strong>SP:</strong> <code>SP_GENERATE_TRF_IN_PLAN</code> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Granularity:</strong> ST_CD + MAJ_CAT + WEEK &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Output Table:</strong> TRF_IN_PLAN</p>
            <p>The algorithm runs a <strong>week-chaining loop</strong> where each week's closing stock becomes the next week's opening stock. Within each week, it calculates shrinkage, net carry-forward, transfer-in need, and closing stock.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Step-by-Step SP Execution -->
    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-3">
        <div class="card-header bg-success bg-opacity-10"><h5 class="card-title mb-0 text-success"><i class="bi bi-list-ol me-2"></i>SP Execution Steps (Inside the Stored Procedure)</h5></div>
        <div class="card-body small">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h6 class="fw-bold">Step 1: Build Week Range</h6>
                    <p class="text-muted">Create <code>#Weeks</code> temp table from <code>WEEK_CALENDAR</code> for @@StartWeekID to @@EndWeekID. Build week offset map (<code>#WkMap</code>) for +1, +2, +3, +4 week lookups.</p>

                    <h6 class="fw-bold">Step 2: Build Store x Category Combinations</h6>
                    <p class="text-muted">Cross join stores from <code>MASTER_ST_MASTER</code> with categories from <code>MASTER_BIN_CAPACITY</code>. Join <code>MASTER_PRODUCT_HIERARCHY</code> for SSN, SEG, DIV metadata.</p>

                    <h6 class="fw-bold">Step 3: UNPIVOT Sale & Display Quantities</h6>
                    <p class="text-muted">UNPIVOT <code>QTY_SALE_QTY</code> (48 weekly columns WK-1..WK-48) into rows. Same for <code>QTY_DISP_QTY</code>. Creates temp tables <code>#SC</code> (sale) and <code>#LS</code> (display) with ST_CD, MAJ_CAT, WK_COL, SALE_QTY/DISP_QTY.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h6 class="fw-bold">Step 4: Build Chain Table</h6>
                    <p class="text-muted">10-column lean temp table per ST_CD + MAJ_CAT + WEEK with: MBQ, SALE, OP_STK, NET_CF, TRF_IN, CL_STK + metadata. Week 1 OP_STK from <code>STORE_STOCK</code> (latest by DATE).</p>

                    <h6 class="fw-bold">Step 5: Week 1 Calculations</h6>
                    <p class="text-muted">Calculate shrinkage, NET_CF, TRF_IN, CL_STK for all store+category combos at once (set-based UPDATE).</p>

                    <h6 class="fw-bold">Step 6: Week 2..N Chaining Loop</h6>
                    <p class="text-muted">WHILE loop: <code>SET OP_STK = prev week CL_STK</code>, then recalculate NET_CF, TRF_IN, CL_STK. All combos updated per week (set-based, not cursor).</p>

                    <h6 class="fw-bold">Step 7: Build Final Output & INSERT</h6>
                    <p class="text-muted">Join chain results with all reference data. Calculate derived columns (excess, short, bin options, DC_MBQ). INSERT into TRF_IN_PLAN.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Core Chain Algorithm -->
    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-3">
        <div class="card-header bg-success bg-opacity-10"><h5 class="card-title mb-0 text-success"><i class="bi bi-link-45deg me-2"></i>Core Chain Algorithm (The Heart of TRF)</h5></div>
        <div class="card-body small">
            <div class="algo-block">
<span class="comment">-- FOR EACH ST_CD + MAJ_CAT + WEEK:</span><br><br>
<span class="keyword">WEEK 1:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">OP_STK</span> = STORE_STOCK.STK_QTY <span class="comment">(latest by DATE for this store+category)</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">MBQ</span> = DISP_QTY(current week) + SALE_QTY(next week) <span class="comment">(Display + Next Week Sale)</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">SALE</span> = SALE_QTY(current week)<br><br>

<span class="keyword">WEEK 2+:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">OP_STK</span> = Previous Week CL_STK <span class="comment">(chained from closing stock)</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">MBQ</span> = DISP_QTY(current week) + SALE_QTY(next week)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">SALE</span> = SALE_QTY(current week)<br><br>

<span class="keyword">ALL WEEKS — Shrinkage Calculation:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;Step 1: <span class="formula">base_shrinkage</span> = ROUND(OP_STK * 0.08, 0) <span class="comment">(8% of opening stock, rounded)</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;Step 2: <span class="formula">SSN_FACTOR</span> = IF SSN IN ('S','PS') THEN <strong>1.0</strong> ELSE <strong>0.5</strong> <span class="comment">(full shrinkage for Summer/Pre-Summer, half for others)</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;Step 3: <span class="formula">SHRINKAGE</span> = ROUND(base_shrinkage * SSN_FACTOR, 0)<br><br>

<span class="keyword">ALL WEEKS — Net Carry-Forward:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">NET_CF</span> = MAX(OP_STK - SHRINKAGE, 0) <span class="comment">(cannot be negative)</span><br><br>

<span class="keyword">ALL WEEKS — Transfer In Quantity:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;IF MBQ = 0 AND SALE = 0 THEN<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">TRF_IN</span> = 0 <span class="comment">(no demand, no transfer needed)</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;ELSE IF MBQ + SALE - NET_CF > 0 THEN<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">TRF_IN</span> = MBQ + SALE - NET_CF <span class="comment">(shortage = transfer in the gap)</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;ELSE<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">TRF_IN</span> = 0 <span class="comment">(enough stock on hand)</span><br><br>

<span class="keyword">ALL WEEKS — Closing Stock:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;IF MBQ = 0 AND SALE = 0 THEN<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">CL_STK</span> = NET_CF <span class="comment">(no demand, carry everything forward)</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;ELSE IF MBQ + SALE > NET_CF THEN<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">CL_STK</span> = MBQ <span class="comment">(demand exceeds stock → after transfer, closing = MBQ buffer)</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;ELSE<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">CL_STK</span> = MAX(NET_CF - SALE, 0) <span class="comment">(enough stock → sell, keep the rest)</span><br>
            </div>
            <div class="alert alert-success py-2 mb-0"><i class="bi bi-arrow-repeat me-1"></i><strong>Week Chaining:</strong> CL_STK of Week N becomes OP_STK of Week N+1. This creates a cascading dependency — every week depends on all prior weeks.</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- All TRF Output Columns -->
    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-3">
        <div class="card-header bg-success bg-opacity-10"><h5 class="card-title mb-0 text-success"><i class="bi bi-table me-2"></i>All TRF_IN_PLAN Output Columns — Complete Formula Reference</h5></div>
        <div class="card-body p-0">
            <div class="table-responsive">
                <table class="table table-sm table-bordered mb-0 small formula-table">
                    <thead class="table-dark"><tr><th>Column</th><th>Formula / Source</th><th>Type</th></tr></thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr><th>ST_CD, ST_NM, RDC_CD, RDC_NM, HUB_CD, HUB_NM, AREA</th><td>From MASTER_ST_MASTER</td><td><span class="badge badge-input">Input</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>MAJ_CAT, SSN, SEG, DIV, SUB_DIV, MAJ_CAT_NM</th><td>From MASTER_BIN_CAPACITY + MASTER_PRODUCT_HIERARCHY</td><td><span class="badge badge-input">Input</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>WEEK_ID, FY_WEEK, FY_YEAR, WK_ST_DT, WK_END_DT</th><td>From WEEK_CALENDAR</td><td><span class="badge badge-input">Input</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>S_GRT_STK_Q</th><td>Always 0</td><td><span class="badge badge-static">Static</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>W_GRT_STK_Q</th><td>IF SSN IN ('W','PW') THEN prev_week_CL_STK ELSE 0</td><td><span class="badge badge-derived">Derived</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>BGT_DISP_CL_Q</th><td>DISP_QTY from QTY_DISP_QTY (unpivoted for current week)</td><td><span class="badge badge-input">Input</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>BGT_DISP_CL_OPT</th><td>ROUND(DISP_QTY * 1000.0 / BIN_CAP, 0)</td><td><span class="badge badge-derived">Derived</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>COVER_SALE_QTY</th><td>Next week sale (SQ1.SALE_QTY)</td><td><span class="badge badge-input">Input</span></td></tr>
                        <tr class="key-formula"><th>BGT_ST_CL_MBQ</th><td><strong>MBQ = DISP_QTY(current) + SALE_QTY(next week)</strong></td><td><span class="badge badge-derived">Derived</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>BGT_DISP_CL_OPT_MBQ</th><td>ROUND(MBQ * 1000.0 / NULLIF(BGT_DISP_CL_OPT, 0), 0)</td><td><span class="badge badge-derived">Derived</span></td></tr>
                        <tr class="key-formula"><th>BGT_TTL_CF_OP_STK_Q</th><td><strong>WK1: STORE_STOCK.STK_QTY &nbsp;|&nbsp; WK2+: prev_CL_STK</strong></td><td><span class="badge badge-chain">Chain</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>NT_ACT_Q (Shrinkage)</th><td>ROUND(ROUND(OP_STK * 0.08, 0) * SSN_FACTOR, 0) &nbsp; SSN_FACTOR: S,PS=1.0; others=0.5</td><td><span class="badge badge-derived">Derived</span></td></tr>
                        <tr class="key-formula"><th>NET_BGT_CF_STK_Q</th><td><strong>MAX(OP_STK - SHRINKAGE, 0)</strong></td><td><span class="badge badge-derived">Derived</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>CM_BGT_SALE_Q</th><td>Current week sale from QTY_SALE_QTY (unpivoted)</td><td><span class="badge badge-input">Input</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>CM1_BGT_SALE_Q</th><td>Next week sale (week+1)</td><td><span class="badge badge-input">Input</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>CM2_BGT_SALE_Q</th><td>Week+2 sale</td><td><span class="badge badge-input">Input</span></td></tr>
                        <tr class="key-formula"><th>TRF_IN_STK_Q</th><td><strong>IF(MBQ=0 AND SALE=0) 0 ELSE MAX(MBQ + SALE - NET_CF, 0)</strong></td><td><span class="badge badge-chain">Chain</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>TRF_IN_OPT_CNT</th><td>ROUND(TRF_IN * 1000.0 / NULLIF(BGT_DISP_CL_OPT_MBQ, 0), 0)</td><td><span class="badge badge-derived">Derived</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>TRF_IN_OPT_MBQ</th><td>TRF_IN * 1000.0 / NULLIF(TRF_IN_OPT_CNT, 0)</td><td><span class="badge badge-derived">Derived</span></td></tr>
                        <tr class="key-formula"><th>DC_MBQ</th><td><strong>SQ1 + SQ2 + SQ3 + SQ4 (sum of next 4 weeks sale)</strong></td><td><span class="badge badge-derived">Derived</span></td></tr>
                        <tr class="key-formula"><th>BGT_TTL_CF_CL_STK_Q</th><td><strong>Closing Stock logic (see algorithm above) — chains to next week</strong></td><td><span class="badge badge-chain">Chain</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>NET_ST_CL_STK_Q</th><td>= CL_STK (same as closing)</td><td><span class="badge badge-derived">Derived</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>ST_CL_EXCESS_Q</th><td>MAX(CL_STK - MBQ, 0)</td><td><span class="badge badge-derived">Derived</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>ST_CL_SHORT_Q</th><td>MAX(MBQ - CL_STK, 0)</td><td><span class="badge badge-derived">Derived</span></td></tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Data Sources -->
