<!-- ║  TAB 4: PURCHASE PLAN ALGORITHM                                 ║ -->
<!-- ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝ -->
<div class="tab-pane fade" id="tabPPAlgo">

    <!-- Algorithm Overview -->
    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-3">
        <div class="card-header" style="background:#8e44ad20;"><h5 class="card-title mb-0" style="color:#8e44ad;"><i class="bi bi-bag-check me-2"></i>Purchase Plan — Complete Algorithm</h5></div>
        <div class="card-body small">
            <p><strong>SP:</strong> <code>SP_GENERATE_PURCHASE_PLAN</code> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Granularity:</strong> RDC_CD + MAJ_CAT + WEEK &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Output Table:</strong> PURCHASE_PLAN</p>
            <p>The Purchase Plan <strong>reads from TRF_IN_PLAN output</strong> — it aggregates all store-level TRF_IN_STK_Q by RDC to get how much stock is being transferred out of each DC. It then runs a DC-level week-chaining loop to determine purchase requirements.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SP Execution Steps -->
    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-3">
        <div class="card-header" style="background:#8e44ad20;"><h5 class="card-title mb-0" style="color:#8e44ad;"><i class="bi bi-list-ol me-2"></i>SP Execution Steps</h5></div>
        <div class="card-body small">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h6 class="fw-bold">Step 1: Build Week Range + Offset Map</h6>
                    <p class="text-muted">Same as TRF — <code>#Weeks</code> and <code>#WkMap</code> with +1 through +5 week offsets.</p>

                    <h6 class="fw-bold">Step 2: Build RDC x MAJ_CAT Combinations</h6>
                    <p class="text-muted">Cross join distinct RDC_CD from ST_MASTER with distinct MAJ_CAT from BIN_CAPACITY. Join PRODUCT_HIERARCHY for SSN.</p>

                    <h6 class="fw-bold">Step 3: Aggregate TRF_IN_PLAN by RDC</h6>
                    <p class="text-muted">GROUP BY RDC_CD, MAJ_CAT, WEEK_ID from <code>TRF_IN_PLAN</code> output. SUMs: TRF_IN_STK_Q → <strong>CW_TRF_OUT_Q</strong>, CM_BGT_SALE_Q, CM1_BGT_SALE_Q, BGT_DISP_CL_Q, BGT_ST_CL_MBQ, etc. Also builds offset tables for CW1-CW4 TRF_OUT and CW2-CW5 SALE.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h6 class="fw-bold">Step 4: Load Reference Data</h6>
                    <p class="text-muted">UNPIVOT <code>MASTER_GRT_CONTRIBUTION</code> (48 WK columns → SSN + WkNum + GrtPct rows). Join DC_STOCK, BIN_CAPACITY, DEL_PENDING for each RDC + MAJ_CAT + WEEK.</p>

                    <h6 class="fw-bold">Step 5: Build #PP Calculation Table</h6>
                    <p class="text-muted">Full join of all data into one temp table with ~50 columns. Initial values set. TTL_TRF_OUT_Q = CW + CW1 + CW2 + CW3 + CW4.</p>

                    <h6 class="fw-bold">Step 6: Week 1 Calculations + Week 2..N Chaining</h6>
                    <p class="text-muted">Calculate all derived columns for Week 1 (set-based). Then WHILE loop chains OP_STK, DC_STK, BGT_CF_STK from previous week's closing values. Recalculates GRT_CONS, PP_NET, POS_PO, NEG_PO, BGT_PUR, BGT_DC_CL_STK per week.</p>

                    <h6 class="fw-bold">Step 7: DELETE old + INSERT into PURCHASE_PLAN</h6>
                    <p class="text-muted">Delete existing rows for this week range + optional RDC/MajCat filter. Insert all calculated rows.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Core PP Algorithm -->
    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-3">
        <div class="card-header" style="background:#8e44ad20;"><h5 class="card-title mb-0" style="color:#8e44ad;"><i class="bi bi-link-45deg me-2"></i>Core DC Chain Algorithm</h5></div>
        <div class="card-body small">
            <div class="algo-block">
<span class="comment">-- FOR EACH RDC_CD + MAJ_CAT + WEEK:</span><br><br>

<span class="keyword">WEEK 1 — Opening Values:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">DC_STK_Q</span> = DC_STOCK table (DC stock for this RDC + MAJ_CAT)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">GRT_STK_Q</span> = DC_STOCK.GRT_STK_Q<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">TTL_STK</span> = GRT_STK_Q <span class="comment">(total stock)</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">OP_STK</span> = GRT_STK_Q <span class="comment">(opening GRT stock)</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">BGT_DC_OP_STK_Q</span> = DC_STK_Q<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">BGT_CF_STK_Q</span> = DC_STK_Q<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">NT_ACT_STK</span> = IF SSN IN ('S','OC','A') THEN GRT_STK_Q * 0.10 ELSE 0<br><br>

<span class="keyword">WEEK 2+ — Chained Values:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">OP_STK</span> = prev_week.NET_SSNL_CL_STK_Q<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">DC_STK_Q</span> = prev_week.BGT_DC_CL_STK_Q<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">BGT_DC_OP_STK_Q</span> = prev_week.BGT_DC_CL_STK_Q<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">BGT_CF_STK_Q</span> = MAX(prev_week.BGT_DC_CL_STK_Q, 0)<br><br>

<span class="keyword">ALL WEEKS — Transfer Out (from TRF_IN_PLAN):</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">CW_TRF_OUT_Q</span> = SUM(TRF_IN_STK_Q) from TRF_IN_PLAN WHERE RDC + MAJ_CAT + current week<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">CW1..CW4_TRF_OUT_Q</span> = same at week offsets +1..+4<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">TTL_TRF_OUT_Q</span> = CW + CW1 + CW2 + CW3 + CW4<br><br>

<span class="keyword">ALL WEEKS — Sale Quantities (from TRF_IN_PLAN aggregation):</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">BGT_DC_MBQ_SALE</span> = CW1_BGT_SALE_Q + CW2_BGT_SALE_Q + CW3_BGT_SALE_Q + CW4_BGT_SALE_Q <span class="comment">(next 4 weeks sale)</span><br><br>

<span class="keyword">ALL WEEKS — DC MBQ:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">BGT_DC_CL_MBQ</span> = MIN(CW1_TRF_OUT + CW2_TRF_OUT + CW3_TRF_OUT + CW4_TRF_OUT, BGT_DC_MBQ_SALE)<br><br>

<span class="keyword">ALL WEEKS — GRT Consumption:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;IF TTL_TRF_OUT_Q = 0 THEN <span class="formula">GRT_CONS_Q</span> = 0<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;ELSE <span class="formula">GRT_CONS_Q</span> = MIN of:<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- TTL_TRF_OUT_Q * 0.30 <span class="comment">(30% of total transfer out)</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- MAX(OP_STK - NT_ACT_STK, 0)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- MAX(TTL_TRF_OUT - MAX(BGT_CF_STK - BGT_DC_CL_MBQ, 0), 0)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- MAX(TTL_STK - NT_ACT_STK, 0) * GRT_CONS_PCT <span class="comment">(from MASTER_GRT_CONTRIBUTION by SSN+Week)</span><br><br>

<span class="keyword">ALL WEEKS — Net & Seasonal:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">PP_NET_BGT_CF_STK_Q</span> = BGT_CF_STK_Q + GRT_CONS_Q + DEL_PEND_Q<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">NET_SSNL_CL_STK_Q</span> = MAX(OP_STK - GRT_CONS_Q, 0)<br><br>

<span class="keyword">ALL WEEKS — Purchase Quantity:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">POS_PO_RAISED</span> = MAX(BGT_DC_CL_MBQ + CW_TRF_OUT_Q - PP_NET_BGT_CF_STK_Q, 0)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">BGT_PUR_Q_INIT</span> = POS_PO_RAISED <span class="comment">(Purchase Order Quantity)</span><br><br>

<span class="keyword">ALL WEEKS — NEG PO (Excess PO):</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="comment">WK-1:</span> <span class="formula">NEG_PO_RAISED</span> = MIN(0, BGT_PUR_Q_INIT - DEL_PEND_Q)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="comment">WK-2+:</span> <span class="formula">NEG_PO_RAISED</span> = MIN(0, BGT_PUR_Q_INIT - DEL_PEND_Q + prev_NEG_PO_RAISED) <span class="comment">(carry-forward accumulation)</span><br><br>

<span class="keyword">ALL WEEKS — DC Closing Stock:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">BGT_DC_CL_STK_Q</span> = MAX(BGT_PUR_Q_INIT + PP_NET_BGT_CF_STK_Q - CW_TRF_OUT_Q, 0)<br><br>

<span class="keyword">ALL WEEKS — Excess / Short:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">DC_STK_EXCESS_Q</span> = MAX(BGT_DC_CL_STK_Q - BGT_DC_CL_MBQ, 0)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">DC_STK_SHORT_Q</span> = MAX(BGT_DC_CL_MBQ - BGT_DC_CL_STK_Q, 0)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">CO_STK_EXCESS_Q</span> = ST_STK_EXCESS_Q + DC_STK_EXCESS_Q<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">CO_STK_SHORT_Q</span> = ST_STK_SHORT_Q + DC_STK_SHORT_Q<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">BGT_CO_CL_STK_Q</span> = NET_BGT_ST_CL_STK_Q + NET_SSNL_CL_STK_Q + BGT_DC_CL_STK_Q<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">FRESH_BIN_REQ</span> = BGT_DC_CL_STK_Q / BIN_CAP<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">GRT_BIN_REQ</span> = OP_STK / BIN_CAP
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

