    <!-- Sub-Level Overview -->
    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-3">
        <div class="card-header" style="background:#e67e2220;"><h5 class="card-title mb-0" style="color:#e67e22;"><i class="bi bi-layers me-2"></i>Sub-Level Plans — Overview</h5></div>
        <div class="card-body small">
            <p>Sub-level plans run the <strong>exact same algorithm</strong> as main plans but at a finer granularity. Instead of ST_CD + MAJ_CAT + WEEK, they add a <strong>SUB_VALUE</strong> dimension representing one of 4 levels:</p>
            <div class="row g-3 mb-3">
                <div class="col-md-3"><div class="card bg-light p-2 text-center"><strong>MVGR</strong><br><small class="text-muted">DISP_MVGR_MATRIX</small><br><code>ST_MAJ_CAT_MACRO_MVGR_PLAN</code></div></div>
                <div class="col-md-3"><div class="card bg-light p-2 text-center"><strong>Size (SZ)</strong><br><small class="text-muted">SZ</small><br><code>ST_MAJ_CAT_SZ_PLAN</code></div></div>
                <div class="col-md-3"><div class="card bg-light p-2 text-center"><strong>Segment (SEG)</strong><br><small class="text-muted">SEG</small><br><code>ST_MAJ_CAT_SEG_PLAN</code></div></div>
                <div class="col-md-3"><div class="card bg-light p-2 text-center"><strong>Vendor (VND)</strong><br><small class="text-muted">M_VND_CD</small><br><code>ST_MAJ_CAT_VND_PLAN</code></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="alert alert-warning py-2 mb-0"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle me-1"></i><strong>Key Difference:</strong> Sub-level plans run <strong>independently</strong> — they do NOT derive from main plan output. They run the full algorithm from scratch using level-specific stock and contribution percentages. Main plan execution is NOT required first (only for sub PP which reads sub TRF).</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- What Changes at Sub-Level -->
    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-3">
        <div class="card-header" style="background:#e67e2220;"><h5 class="card-title mb-0" style="color:#e67e22;"><i class="bi bi-arrow-left-right me-2"></i>What Changes vs Main Plan</h5></div>
        <div class="card-body p-0 small">
            <div class="table-responsive">
                <table class="table table-sm table-bordered mb-0">
                    <thead class="table-dark"><tr><th>Aspect</th><th>Main Plan</th><th>Sub-Level Plan</th></tr></thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr><td class="fw-bold">Granularity</td><td>ST_CD + MAJ_CAT + WEEK</td><td>ST_CD + MAJ_CAT + <strong>SUB_VALUE</strong> + WEEK</td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="fw-bold">Sale Qty</td><td>Direct from QTY_SALE_QTY</td><td>SALE_QTY <strong>x CONT_PCT</strong> from contribution table</td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="fw-bold">Display Qty</td><td>Direct from QTY_DISP_QTY</td><td>DISP_QTY <strong>x CONT_PCT</strong> from contribution table</td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="fw-bold">Store Stock (TRF)</td><td>From <code>STORE_STOCK</code></td><td>From <code>SUB_ST_STK_{MVGR|SZ|SEG|VND}</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="fw-bold">DC Stock (PP)</td><td>From <code>DC_STOCK</code></td><td>From <code>SUB_DC_STK_{MVGR|SZ|SEG|VND}</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="fw-bold">TRF Algorithm</td><td>Same chain logic</td><td><strong>Identical</strong> — shrinkage, NET_CF, TRF_IN, CL_STK</td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="fw-bold">PP Algorithm</td><td>GRT_CONS uses GRT_CONS_PCT from MASTER_GRT_CONTRIBUTION</td><td>GRT_CONS_Q = 0 (simplified — no GRT_CONS_PCT at sub-level)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="fw-bold">PP reads from</td><td>TRF_IN_PLAN</td><td>SUB_LEVEL_TRF_PLAN (same level)</td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="fw-bold">Output Tables</td><td>TRF_IN_PLAN, PURCHASE_PLAN</td><td>SUB_LEVEL_TRF_PLAN, SUB_LEVEL_PP_PLAN</td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="fw-bold">Bin Rounding</td><td>TRF_IN rounded to BIN_CAP multiples (opt calculations)</td><td>No bin rounding (raw TRF_IN quantity)</td></tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Sub TRF Algorithm -->
    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-3">
        <div class="card-header" style="background:#27ae6020;"><h5 class="card-title mb-0 text-success"><i class="bi bi-calculator me-2"></i>Sub-Level TRF Algorithm (SP_GENERATE_SUB_LEVEL_TRF)</h5></div>
        <div class="card-body small">
            <div class="algo-block">
<span class="keyword">INPUT PREPARATION:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;1. Get contribution % from <span class="formula">ST_MAJ_CAT_{LEVEL}_PLAN</span> table (dynamic table name based on @@Level)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;2. UNPIVOT QTY_SALE_QTY (48 WK cols → rows), multiply by <span class="formula">CONT_PCT</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;3. UNPIVOT QTY_DISP_QTY (48 WK cols → rows), multiply by <span class="formula">CONT_PCT</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;4. Load store stock from <span class="formula">SUB_ST_STK_{LEVEL}</span> (latest by DATE, per ST_CD + MAJ_CAT + SUB_VALUE)<br><br>

<span class="keyword">CHAIN TABLE (per ST_CD + MAJ_CAT + SUB_VALUE + WEEK):</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">MBQ</span> = (DISP_QTY * CONT_PCT) + (SALE_QTY_next_week * CONT_PCT)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">SALE</span> = SALE_QTY_current_week * CONT_PCT<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">OP_STK</span> = WK1: SUB_ST_STK_{level}.STK_QTY &nbsp;|&nbsp; WK2+: prev CL_STK<br><br>

<span class="keyword">SAME FORMULAS AS MAIN TRF:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">SHRINKAGE</span> = ROUND(ROUND(OP_STK * 0.08, 0) * SSN_FACTOR, 0)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">NET_CF</span> = MAX(OP_STK - SHRINKAGE, 0)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">TRF_IN</span> = IF(MBQ=0 AND SALE=0) 0 ELSE MAX(MBQ + SALE - NET_CF, 0)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">CL_STK</span> = IF(no demand) NET_CF ELSE IF(demand>stock) MBQ ELSE MAX(NET_CF-SALE,0)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">DC_MBQ</span> = SQ1 + SQ2 + SQ3 + SQ4 (sum of next 4 weeks sale * CONT_PCT)<br><br>

<span class="keyword">OUTPUT → SUB_LEVEL_TRF_PLAN</span> with LEVEL column = @@Level
            </div>

            <h6 class="fw-bold mt-3">Sub TRF Output Columns</h6>
            <div class="table-responsive">
                <table class="table table-sm table-bordered mb-0 formula-table">
                    <thead class="table-dark"><tr><th>Column</th><th>Formula</th><th>Level-Specific?</th></tr></thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr class="changed"><th>BGT_DISP_CL_Q</th><td>DISP_QTY (UNPIVOT) x CONT_PCT</td><td><span class="badge bg-success">Yes</span></td></tr>
                        <tr class="changed"><th>CM_BGT_SALE_Q</th><td>SALE_QTY (UNPIVOT) x CONT_PCT</td><td><span class="badge bg-success">Yes</span></td></tr>
                        <tr class="changed"><th>CM1_BGT_SALE_Q</th><td>SALE_QTY (week+1) x CONT_PCT</td><td><span class="badge bg-success">Yes</span></td></tr>
                        <tr class="changed"><th>CM2_BGT_SALE_Q</th><td>SALE_QTY (week+2) x CONT_PCT</td><td><span class="badge bg-success">Yes</span></td></tr>
                        <tr class="changed"><th>COVER_SALE_QTY</th><td>CM + CM1 + CM2 + CM3 (4 weeks sale x CONT_PCT)</td><td><span class="badge bg-success">Yes</span></td></tr>
                        <tr class="changed"><th>BGT_TTL_CF_OP_STK_Q</th><td>WK1: SUB_ST_STK_{level} &nbsp;|&nbsp; WK2+: prev CL_STK</td><td><span class="badge bg-success">Yes</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>SHRINKAGE (NT_ACT_Q)</th><td>ROUND(ROUND(OP * 0.08) * SSN_FACTOR) — same formula</td><td><span class="badge bg-warning text-dark">Same</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>NET_BGT_CF_STK_Q</th><td>MAX(OP - SHRINKAGE, 0) — same formula</td><td><span class="badge bg-warning text-dark">Same</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>BGT_ST_CL_MBQ</th><td>MBQ = DISP*CONT + SALE_next*CONT</td><td><span class="badge bg-success">Yes</span></td></tr>
                        <tr class="key-formula"><th>TRF_IN_STK_Q</th><td><strong>MAX(MBQ + SALE - NET_CF, 0)</strong> — same formula, different inputs</td><td><span class="badge bg-success">Yes</span></td></tr>
                        <tr class="key-formula"><th>BGT_TTL_CF_CL_STK_Q</th><td><strong>Closing stock — chains to next week</strong></td><td><span class="badge bg-success">Yes</span></td></tr>
                        <tr><th>ST_CL_EXCESS_Q / ST_CL_SHORT_Q</th><td>MAX(CL-MBQ, 0) / MAX(MBQ-CL, 0)</td><td><span class="badge bg-success">Yes</span></td></tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Sub PP Algorithm -->
    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-3">
        <div class="card-header" style="background:#8e44ad20;"><h5 class="card-title mb-0" style="color:#8e44ad;"><i class="bi bi-calculator me-2"></i>Sub-Level PP Algorithm (SP_GENERATE_SUB_LEVEL_PP)</h5></div>
        <div class="card-body small">
            <div class="algo-block">
<span class="keyword">INPUT — Reads from SUB_LEVEL_TRF_PLAN (must run TRF first per level):</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;Aggregates by RDC_CD + MAJ_CAT + SUB_VALUE + WEEK from SUB_LEVEL_TRF_PLAN WHERE LEVEL = @@Level<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;CW_TRF_OUT_Q = SUM(TRF_IN_STK_Q) grouped by RDC<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;CW1-CW4 TRF_OUT at week offsets +1..+4<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;CW1-CW4 SALE at week offsets<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;DC stock from <span class="formula">SUB_DC_STK_{LEVEL}</span> (latest by DATE, per RDC + MAJ_CAT + SUB_VALUE)<br><br>

<span class="keyword">WEEK 1:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">OP_STK</span> = GRT_STK_Q from SUB_DC_STK<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">BGT_DC_OP_STK_Q</span> = DC_STK_Q from SUB_DC_STK<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">GRT_CONS_Q</span> = 0 <span class="comment">(simplified — no GRT_CONS_PCT at sub-level)</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">PP_NET_BGT_CF_STK_Q</span> = BGT_CF_STK_Q + GRT_CONS_Q <span class="comment">(no DEL_PEND at sub-level)</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">NET_SSNL_CL_STK_Q</span> = MAX(OP_STK - GRT_CONS_Q, 0)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">POS_PO_RAISED</span> = MAX(BGT_DC_CL_MBQ + CW_TRF_OUT_Q - PP_NET_BGT_CF_STK_Q, 0)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">BGT_PUR_Q_INIT</span> = POS_PO_RAISED<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">NEG_PO_RAISED</span> = MIN(0, BGT_PUR_Q_INIT - DEL_PEND_Q)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">BGT_DC_CL_STK_Q</span> = MAX(BGT_PUR_Q_INIT + PP_NET_BGT_CF_STK_Q - CW_TRF_OUT_Q, 0)<br><br>

<span class="keyword">WEEK 2+:</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">OP_STK</span> = prev_week.NET_SSNL_CL_STK_Q<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">DC_STK_Q</span> = prev_week.BGT_DC_CL_STK_Q<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">BGT_CF_STK_Q</span> = MAX(prev_week.BGT_DC_CL_STK_Q, 0)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="formula">NEG_PO_RAISED</span> = MIN(0, BGT_PUR_Q_INIT - DEL_PEND_Q + prev_NEG_PO_RAISED)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="comment">... all other formulas identical to Week 1</span><br><br>

<span class="keyword">OUTPUT → SUB_LEVEL_PP_PLAN</span> with LEVEL column = @@Level
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

