    <!-- Execution Flow -->
    <div class="card shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-header" style="background:#e67e2220;"><h5 class="card-title mb-0" style="color:#e67e22;"><i class="bi bi-diagram-3 me-2"></i>Sub-Level Execution Flow</h5></div>
        <div class="card-body small">
            <div class="algo-block">
<span class="keyword">FOR EACH SELECTED LEVEL</span> (MVGR, SZ, SEG, VND):<br><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="keyword">STEP 1:</span> Run <span class="formula">SP_GENERATE_SUB_LEVEL_TRF</span>(@@Level, @@StartWeek, @@EndWeek)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;→ Reads: contribution table, sub store stock, sale*CONT%, display*CONT%<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;→ Writes: SUB_LEVEL_TRF_PLAN WHERE LEVEL = @@Level<br><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="keyword">STEP 2:</span> Run <span class="formula">SP_GENERATE_SUB_LEVEL_PP</span>(@@Level, @@StartWeek, @@EndWeek)<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;→ Reads: SUB_LEVEL_TRF_PLAN (output from Step 1), sub DC stock<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;→ Writes: SUB_LEVEL_PP_PLAN WHERE LEVEL = @@Level<br><br>
<span class="keyword">FULL RUN (Background):</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;SubLevelJobService runs above steps for all 4 levels <span class="formula">sequentially</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;Progress tracking: Phase (TRF/PP), CurrentLevel, LevelsCompleted/TotalLevels<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;Polled via SubJobStatus endpoint every 5 seconds
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

